MapperVersion: The dataset focuses on vascular plants collected in support of an Ecology and Biodiversity of Cambridge Bay, Victoria Island, Nunavut project.The field work was confined to southeast Victoria Island, mostly within walking distance of the road network along the southeast island. Most field sessions were brief with the objective of gaining some initial observations. Collections were made for verification and in support of a core vascular plant reference collection for the Canadian High Arctic Research Station (CHARS) at Cambridge Bay, Nunavut.
